arStrings.szText: "Have you seen an old woman in an orange scarf?"
Suna...yes, it happened last night. The Penitent ones arrested her on suspicion of heresy. They’ve been hunting for someone. Rounding people up for days to interrogate them.
Afraid of the consequences of speaking, but unwilling to remain silent. Hoping the player can be trusted.
They have a house they’ve taken over, near the center of town. Hmm... You’ll never get in though, they guard it day and night.
